<h1  style=" text-align: center;" >SEARCH ENGINE OPYIMIZATTION</h1>
<div class="d-md-flex flex-md-equal w-100 my-md-3 ps-md-3">
  
<img  class ="seotext " src="https://monsterspost.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/free-pesto-cafe-restaurant-website-template.jpg" alt="" style="margin:  auto "   > 

</div>
